lead_paragraph: The former president of the German soccer federation can continue to refer to Qatar as a "cancerous growth of world football" — at least until a final ruling by a German court.

headline.print_headline: Former German Soccer President Wins Preliminary Court Ruling
headline.main: Former German Soccer President Wins Preliminary Court Ruling
